<li id="cite_note-27"><b><a href="#cite_ref-27" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFChomsky1999">Chomsky, Noam (1999). <i>Profit Over People: Neoliberalism and Global Order</i>. New York, New York, United States: Seven Stories Press. pp.&#160;175. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781888363821" class="internal">ISBN 978-1-888363-82-1</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Profit+Over+People%3A+Neoliberalism+and+Global+Order&amp;rft.aulast=Chomsky&amp;rft.aufirst=Noam&amp;rft.au=Chomsky%2C+Noam&amp;rft.date=1999&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B175&amp;rft.place=New+York%2C+New+York%2C+United+States&amp;rft.pub=Seven+Stories+Press&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-888363-82-1&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Corporation"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
